---
import AppShell from "@cyan/layouts/AppShell.astro";
---

<AppShell title="Cyan Design System" layout="sidebar">
  <nav slot="tray">
    <h4>Main menu</h4>
    <a href="#">Foundations</a>
    <a href="#">Components</a>
    <a href="#">Patterns</a>
  </nav>

  <h1>Cyan Design System</h1>
  <p>
    Cyan Design System is a custom UI component library built for <a href="https://pelilauta.social">pelilauta.social</a>.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    For its fourth major redesign, the system is implemented using Astro components for structural SSR and Svelte 5 for interactive client-side progressive enhancement.
  </p>

  <h2>Source code and licensing</h2>
  <p>
    Most parts of the design system are licensed under the MIT license. Please check individual plugins and components for their independent licensing info.
  </p>

  <p>
    All source code is managed as an internal package within the Pelilauta 20 pnpm workspace.
  </p>
</AppShell>
